        section: "Organization and Integration of Components",
        classOfRec: "I",
        classNote: null,
        levelOfEvidence: "B-NR",
        text: "PSC facilities that rely on interfacility transfers for thrombectomy are recommended to have rapid intracranial vascular imaging capability (CTA or MRA) to identify LVO patients eligible for EVT.",
