        classOfRec: "I",
        classNote: null,
        levelOfEvidence: "B-R",
        text: "Facilities providing EVT (TSC, CSC) are recommended to comprehensively track key time metrics and care processes relevant to thrombectomy (e.g., door-to-puncture time, reperfusion success) as well as long-term patient outcomes.",
