        classOfRec: "IIa",
        classNote: null,
        levelOfEvidence: "B-NR",
        text: "ASRHs that rely on interfacility transfers can consider having the capability to rapidly perform and interpret intracranial vascular imaging (CTA or MRA) to identify LVO patients eligible for EVT.",
