        section: "Organization and Integration of Components",
        classOfRec: "IIb",
        classNote: null,
        levelOfEvidence: "B-NR",
        text: "Depending on local and regional systems of care characteristics, individual stroke systems may consider developing mobile intervention teams to improve timely EVT delivery.",
