        section: "Stroke Registries, Quality Improvement, and",
        classOfRec: "I",
        classNote: null,
        levelOfEvidence: "B-NR",
        text: "Participation in stroke data registries is recommended for facilities treating acute stroke patients to increase adherence to quality indicators and guideline recommendations and improve patient outcomes.",
