        section: "Initial, Vascular, and Multimodal Imaging",
        classOfRec: "I",
        classNote: null,
        levelOfEvidence: "B-NR",
        text: "Facilities caring for suspected AIS patients are recommended to establish process improvement protocols so emergent brain imaging can be performed as rapidly as possible (e.g., within 25 minutes) to facilitate timely reperfusion interventions.",
