        classOfRec: "IIa",
        classNote: null,
        levelOfEvidence: "C-LD",
        text: "In pediatric patients with suspected AIS, emergent brain and vascular imaging with MRI/MRA of the cervical and intracranial vessels is reasonable to identify LVO and differentiate arterial ischemic stroke from hemorrhagic stroke or stroke mimics.",
