        classOfRec: "IIa",
        classNote: null,
        levelOfEvidence: "C-LD",
        text: "In pediatric patients with suspected AIS, emergent CT/CTA of the cervical and intracranial vessels is reasonable when MRI/MRA is not immediately available (within 25 minutes) to identify LVO.",
