        classOfRec: "IIa",
        classNote: null,
        levelOfEvidence: "B-R",
        text: "In patients with suspected AIS who awaken with symptoms or have unknown time of onset beyond 4.5 hours from last known well but are otherwise eligible for thrombolysis, MRI DWI-FLAIR mismatch selection can be useful to determine eligibility for extended-window IVT.",
