        classOfRec: "IIa",
        classNote: null,
        levelOfEvidence: "B-R",
        text: "In patients with suspected AIS who awaken with symptoms or have unknown time of onset 4.5 to 24 hours from last known well, CTP or MR DWI-PWI selection with automated postprocessing software can be useful to determine eligibility for extended-window IVT.",
