        text: "In patients with suspected AIS and LVO presenting within 24 hours of last known well, emergent brain and vascular imaging (CT/CTA or MRI/MRA) of the cervical and intracranial vessels is recommended to be performed as rapidly as possible for EVT selection and treatment planning.",
