        text: "In patients with suspected AIS and LVO presenting 6 to 24 hours from last known well, adjunctive CTP, MRI (DWI-FLAIR mismatch), or MR DWI-PWI with automated postprocessing software can be useful in EVT evaluation if immediately available.",
