        classOfRec: "IIb",
        classNote: null,
        levelOfEvidence: "B-R",
        text: "In patients with suspected AIS and LVO identified by prefacility assessment with a validated stroke severity scale (e.g., RACE >4) who are EVT-eligible, direct triage to the angiography suite for flat-panel head CT may be considered to reduce time to intervention and improve functional outcomes compared with conventional imaging workflow.",
