        classOfRec: "IIb",
        classNote: null,
        levelOfEvidence: "B-NR",
        text: "In emergently transferred patients with suspected AIS due to LVO who are EVT-eligible, direct triage to the angiography suite may be considered without repeat brain imaging on arrival at the thrombectomy center, unless there is clinical change or transfer delay.",
